This directory contains the reference implementation of the SnuPL/2 scanner (scanner.o)

To use this scanner instead of your own, perform the following steps:

1. create a directory 'lib' under 'snuplc'
   $ mkdir ../../lib

2. copy scanner.o to the newly created directory
   $ cp scanner.o ../../lib/

3. copy scanner.h to the source directory
   $ cp scanner.h ../../src/

4. replace the Makefile in snuplc/ with Makefile.lib in this directory
   $ cp Makefile.lib ../../Makefile


